#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define ll long long

int main()
{
    int t;
    ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
    cin.tie(0);
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        ll n;
        cin>>n;
        ll a[n+1];
        for(ll i=0;i<n;i++)
        cin>>a[i];
        sort(a,a+n);
        ll ans=__gcd(a[0],a[1]);
        for(ll i=2;i<n;i++){
        ans = __gcd(ans,a[i]);if(ans==1)break;}
        cout<<ans<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
